Get the original matrix

get_matrix-ConsensusPartition-method.Rd

Get the original matrix

# S4 method for ConsensusPartition
get_matrix(object)

Arguments

object

A ConsensusPartition-class object.

Value

A numeric matrix.

Examples

data(golub_cola)
obj = golub_cola["ATC", "skmeans"]
get_matrix(obj)
